snippet: Every network was down substantially from its view levels of four years ago, suggesting a deep lack of interest in the results.
abstract: Fox News draws biggest audience for its coverage of midterm elections, beating not only cable competitors but also beating broadcast networks' limited coverage.

headline.main: Fox Election Coverage Draws Biggest Share of a Less-Than-Rapt Audience
headline.print_headline: Of the Few Who Tuned in, More Turned to Fox News
